  "title": "Introduction to Cold Sensations and Fever",
  "lessonText": "Understanding cold sensations and fever is crucial for effective health management.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Cold sensations can indicate various health issues.\n- Fever is a common response to infection.\n- Identifying symptoms helps in determining the underlying cause.\n- Early recognition can lead to timely treatment."
